00:42:53,287 --> 00:42:55,243
"Darling"?

477
00:42:56,727 --> 00:42:58,683
"Dear Vera."

478
00:43:02,167 --> 00:43:04,362
"Vera."

479
00:43:04,487 --> 00:43:08,958
"I know that the cruel joke you played on
