referring to the game I played on Colin.

529
00:47:06,807 --> 00:47:07,956
- Yeah.
- Good.

530
00:47:08,087 --> 00:47:11,966
Now we've established
your name and what you're talking about,

531
00:47:12,087 --> 00:47:15,796
